config ZMK_INPUT_PROCESSOR_TRACKBALL_THRESHOLD
    bool "Trackball threshold input processor"
    default y
    help
      Enable trackball movement threshold filtering input processor.
      This processor filters out small trackball movements below a configurable threshold,
      preventing accidental auto mouse layer activation from minor vibrations.

config ZMK_INPUT_PROCESSOR_TRACKBALL_THRESHOLD_DEFAULT_THRESHOLD
    int "Default movement threshold"
    default 5
    range 0 1000
    depends on ZMK_INPUT_PROCESSOR_TRACKBALL_THRESHOLD
    help
      Default threshold value for trackball movement filtering.
      Movement is calculated as abs(x) + abs(y).
      Values below this threshold will be discarded. 